<div id="keynote">
  <h2>Emoti-Con 2020 Keynote by Errol King</h2>
  <p>Errol King is the Keynote for the 12th annual Emoti-Con NYC Youth Digital Media & Technology Challenge (www.emoti-con.org). In this interview, Errol shares his pathway from teenager from the Bronx to Creative Technologist at Google.  We learn about his experience working remotely, his philosophy about learning, creativity, co-creation and the importance of patience.</p>
